Install Web

1. Create a directory and put peg.py, excuses.txt and templates/template.html


To install as a service

1. Install waitress globally 
        sudo python -m pip install waitress

2. copy lunch.service to /etc/systemd/system/

3. Edit lunch.service to match your path with working directory and the correct user.  Please do not use root. 

4. Run sudo systemctl daemon-reload

5. Run sudo systemctl start lunch

6. Now check if service is working with  sudo systemctl status lunch




Enjoy 

